      "comment": "INFRARED POWER (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 18.57 beating Territory Man. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Can make it two on the bounce. ROOSTER JAZZ (8) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (18.36) from Box 5 at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and three minor placings from 10 starts. Bold showing expected. MUM'S BOY (5) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing second and beaten 1.5 lengths (18.32) behind Territory Tuff at this track. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Will give a great sight again. MISH MASH (4) was in the money again last time and not beaten far when second (18.35) at this track in a Grade 4.",
